OL,3,CGuernsey names Brittany Ferries as
OL,4,Cpreferred ferry operator
OL,6,FThe Committee for Economic Development
OL,7,Fin Guernsey has selected Brittany
OL,8,FFerries as the preferred bidder to
OL,9,Fprovide sea links for the island.
OL,11,FAt this stage Guernsey and Jersey have
OL,12,Fnot reached a shared view on how to
OL,13,Fproceed, but it follows a bidding
OL,14,Fprocess that's been taking place over
OL,15,Fthe last 10 months.
