OL,3,CGuernsey names Brittany Ferries as
OL,4,Cpreferred ferry operator
OL,6,FGuernsey's preference remains a shared
OL,7,Fpan Channel Island service with
OL,8,FJersey, but they say they are
OL,9,F"awaiting word from their Jersey
OL,10,Fpartners" which they expect tomorrow
OL,11,F(Thursday 31 October).
OL,13,FDeputy Neil Inder, President of the
OL,14,FCommittee for Economic Development,
OL,15,Fsaid: "Over the past 10 months we have
OL,16,Fundertaken a joint tender exercise
OL,17,Fwith the Government of Jersey for the
OL,18,FIsland's critical lifeline sea links.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
