OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1730396100
OL,3,CGuernsey names Brittany Ferries as
OL,4,Cpreferred ferry operator
OL,6,F"The tender process has been robust,
OL,7,Fand the Committee has reached an
OL,8,Fevidence-based conclusion. On that
OL,9,Fbasis the Committee has decided
OL,10,Funanimously to appoint Brittany
OL,11,FFerries as its preferred bidder,
OL,12,Fsubject to further negotiations on
OL,13,Fsome elements of the contract.
OL,15,F"At this stage Guernsey and Jersey
OL,16,Fhave not reached a shared view on how
OL,17,Fto proceed. That is not for me to
OL,18,Fcomment on, and I understand political
OL,19,Fdiscussions in Jersey are ongoing.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
