OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1730396100
OL,3,CGuernsey names Brittany Ferries as
OL,4,Cpreferred ferry operator
OL,6,F"All I can say at this stage is that
OL,7,Fwhile both islands share common
OL,8,Fobjectives, agreement has not yet been
OL,9,Freached on the best way to jointly
OL,10,Fdeliver those objectives."
OL,12,FHe added: "The Committee has not taken
OL,13,Fthe decision to push ahead alone at
OL,14,Fthis stage lightly, but following the
OL,15,Fobjective evaluation process Brittany
OL,16,FFerries' bid was successful and we are
OL,17,Fcommitted to providing certainty to
OL,18,Fislanders as soon as we were able to
OL,19,Fdo so.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
