OL,3,CGuernsey names Brittany Ferries as
OL,4,Cpreferred ferry operator
OL,6,F"An arrangement will be put in place
OL,7,Fwith Brittany Ferries which leaves the
OL,8,Fdoor open for Jersey if Jersey does
OL,9,Fdecide to seek a different approach.
OL,10,FThis outcome is not a failure of the
OL,11,Ftender process. The process has
OL,12,Fenabled us to consider and test a
OL,13,Fnumber of different options and secure
OL,14,Fthe best possible deal for islanders.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
