OL,3,CGuernsey names Brittany Ferries as
OL,4,Cpreferred ferry operator
OL,6,F"If we do move to a Guernsey-only
OL,7,Fservice from Brittany Ferries, the new
OL,8,Farrangement would mean that the way
OL,9,Fthat some services operate will be
OL,10,Fchanged, but we will have the same
OL,11,Ffreight and passenger capacity for our
OL,12,Fcommunity, improved resilience in the
OL,13,Ffleet, and the benefit of Brittany
OL,14,FFerries' expertise, willingness to
OL,15,Finnovate, and commitment to improved
OL,16,Fcustomer services."
