OL,3,CGuernsey names Brittany Ferries as
OL,4,Cpreferred ferry operator
OL,6,FBrittany and Condor Ferries say they
OL,7,Fare "thrilled" at the announcement and
OL,8,Fthat they "look forward to the
OL,9,FGovernment of Jersey joining us in
OL,10,Fthis initiative".
OL,12,FHowever, by Wednesday evening, it
OL,13,Fseemed unclear when or if Jersey would
OL,14,Fbe making a decision imminently.
OL,16,FThe island's Minister for Sustainable
OL,17,FEconomic Development, Deputy Kirsten
OL,18,FMorel, said: "For 15 years, we're
OL,19,Fgoing to have one provider. We need to
OL,20,Fknow we can rely on that provider come
OL,21,Fwhat may.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
