OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1730396100
OL,3,CGuernsey names Brittany Ferries as
OL,4,Cpreferred ferry operator
OL,6,F"And I think that's really where the
OL,7,Fproblem was. Guernsey obviously didn't
OL,8,Fthink they needed any more
OL,9,Finformation. In Jersey, I think quite
OL,10,Frightly, we did feel we needed more
OL,11,Finformation."
OL,13,FIt follows calls for an imminent
OL,14,Fdecision to be made from tourism
OL,15,Findustry leaders who said an
OL,16,F"unacceptable delay" was putting
OL,17,Fpressure on the sector.
